Ah, Milly D'Abbraccio!  Lusty Italian lady.  The premise of this rather gonzo flick is simple...Milly is bored with Italian men and wants to explore the United States.  So she does.  Sex in a limo, a threesome, an orgy, and an oddly inserted scene between two pre-op transsexuals.

There's nothing unusual about this movie.  It's a competently-shot adult film with a fair variety of couplings, with appropriate close-ups and the requisite money shots.

The actors, I don't recognize, aside from Milly.  As they're all speaking Italian, it's reasonable to believe that they are not, in fact, the Americans Milly sought out, but I was able to look past this and enjoy the movie.
